description: This file defines the interface and exported functions for an SNMP plugin component related to the Advanced Networking Service Container (ANSC). It declares function prototypes for initialization, support checks, unload, and memory management, and includes license and module information.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the SNMP plugin with the maximum supported version and plugin info.

methods.name: COSA_Async_Init
methods.description: Asynchronous initialization of the SNMP plugin.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjectSupported
methods.description: Checks if a given object name is supported by the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Unloads or cleans up resources related to the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_MemoryCheck
methods.description: Performs a memory check for the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_MemoryUsage
methods.description: Reports the memory usage of the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_MemoryTable
methods.description: Outputs or manages the plugin's memory table.
